what you thought?

449
00:23:25,621 --> 00:23:27,947
But I'm not here to think.

450
00:23:27,971 --> 00:23:30,994
I'm here to take the minutes
of your meeting.

451
00:23:31,018 --> 00:23:33,257
But if in your entire life
you truly felt

452
00:23:33,281 --> 00:23:35,172
it didn't matter
what you thought,

453
00:23:35,196 --> 00:23:36,893
how would that make you feel?

454
00:23:47,295 --> 00:23:48,620
When we've liberated ourselves,

455
00:23:48,644 --> 00:23:51,168
we will have to ask ourselves
who we are.

456
00:23:52,431 --> 00:23:53,693
[Somber music playing]

457
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:01,440
[Sighs]

458
