one of your friends.

519
00:28:08,382 --> 00:28:10,993
I think it
was likely yours though...

520
00:28:13,430 --> 00:28:15,452
Because there was something
wrong with it.

521
00:28:15,476 --> 00:28:16,956
[Eerie music playing]

522
